BriefDescription: This event counts operations that cause a TLB refill of the L1I TLB. See L1I_TLB_REFILL of ARMv9 Reference Manual for more information.
This event counts operations that cause a TLB refill of the L1D TLB. See L1D_TLB_REFILL of ARMv9 Reference Manual for more information.
This event counts operations that cause a TLB access to the L1D TLB. See L1D_TLB of ARMv9 Reference Manual for more information.
This event counts operations that cause a TLB access to the L1I TLB. See L1I_TLB of ARMv9 Reference Manual for more information.
This event counts operations that cause a TLB refill of the L2D TLB. See L2D_TLB_REFILL of ARMv9 Reference Manual for more information.
This event counts operations that cause a TLB access to the L2D TLB. See L2D_TLB of ARMv9 Reference Manual for more information.
This event counts data TLB access with at least one translation table walk.
This event counts instruction TLB access with at least one translation table walk.
This event counts operations that cause a TLB access to the L1I in 4KB page.
